ersion":"silver","text":"Its tail, which also contains a small brain, may bite on its own if it notices an alluring smell."},{"version":"crystal","text":"When it is in danger, its tail uses some sort of mysterious powers to drive away the enemy."},{"version":"ruby","text":"GIRAFARIG\u2019s rear head also has a brain, but it is small. The rear head attacks in response to smells and sounds. Approaching this POK\u00e9MON from behind can cause the rear head to suddenly lash out and bite."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"GIRAFARIG\u2019s rear head contains a tiny brain that is too small for thinking. However, the rear head doesn\u2019t need to sleep, so it can keep watch over its surroundings 24 hours a day."},{"version":"emerald","text":"A GIRAFARIG is an herbivore--it eats grass and tree shoots. While it is eating, its tail makes chewing and swallowing motions as if it were also eating."},{"version":"firered","text":"Its tail, which also contains a small brain, may bite on its own if it notices an alluring smell."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"Its tail has a small brain of its own. Beware! If you get close, it may react to your scent and bite."},{"version":"diamond","text":"Its tail also has a small brain. It bites to repel any foe trying to sneak up on it from behind."},{"version":"pearl","text":"While it sleeps, the head on its tail keeps watch. The tail doesn\u2019t need to sleep."},{"version":"platinum","text":"The head on its tail contains a small brain. It can instinctively fight even while facing backward."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"Its tail has a small brain of its own. Beware! If you get close, it may react to your scent by biting."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"Its tail, which also contains a small brain, may bite on its own if it notices an alluring smell."},{"version":"black","text":"The head on its tail contains a small brain. It can instinctively fight even while facing backward."},{"version":"white","text":"The head on its tail contains a small brain. It can instinctively fight even while facing backward."},{"version":"black-2","text":"The head on its tail contains a small brain. It can instinctively fight even while facing backward."},{"version":"white-2","text":"The head on its tail contains a small brain. It can instinctively fight even while facing backward."},{"version":"x","text":"While it sleeps, the head on its tail keeps watch. The tail doesn\u2019t need to sleep."},{"version":"y","text":"Its tail has a small brain of its own. Beware! If you get close, it may react to your scent by biting."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Girafarig\u2019s rear head also has a brain, but it is small. The rear head attacks in response to smells and sounds. Approaching this Pok\u00e9mon from behind can cause the rear head to suddenly lash out and bite."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Girafarig\u2019s rear head contains a tiny brain that is too small for thinking. However, the rear head doesn\u2019t need to sleep, so it can keep watch over its surroundings 24 hours a day."}],"evo":{"name":"girafarig","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"farigiraf","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":"twin-beam","known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/203.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/shiny/203.png","capture":60,"happiness":70,"growth":"medium","gender":4,"hatch":20,"ev":{"special_attack":2},"forms":[]}